Lorenz Attractor Visualization
==============================
Author: Sanjay Baskaran
Course: Computer Graphics (CSCI-x229) – Homework X (Lorenz)

Build:
  make      # builds 'lorenz'
  make clean

Controls:
  Arrow Keys    Rotate camera
  PageUp/PageDn Zoom in/out
  s/S           Decrease/Increase σ
  b/B           Decrease/Increase β
  r/R           Decrease/Increase ρ
  a/A           Toggle axes
  0             Reset parameters & view
  q or ESC      Quit

Features:
  - Perspective projection with depth buffer ensures no distortion on resize
  - Interactive parameter tuning regenerates trajectory in real time
  - Smooth color trace of attractor and optional axes

Time Spent:
  ~6 hours (implementation & testing)